Partial transcript of telephone conversation between O5-2 and O5-13.
------

**O5-13:** How many confirmed containment breaches?

**O5-2:** We’re unsure. Of 563 worldwide secure facilities, only 32 remain online. But that’s with the data we have, SCiPNET’s entirely down. We tapped ground communications, there’s breaches in almost every major city and emergency service lines are flooded, on top of what’s happening with the moon. All Task Forces are deployed, but it’s not enough. -6 and -10 are contacting known Groups of Interest. 

**O5-13:** Fucking hell. Are sites maintaining their power? If not, the nuclear failsafes are going to–

**O5-2:** The system’s been overridden using the Administrator’s master commands. It’s not our nukes we should be worried about.

